It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* with *Broadridge*. I bring over three years of professional experience building backend systems, automated test pipelines, and production-grade Java and Python applications, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

